embeds.title: Phene
embeds.description:
Hey, I'm Phene.

I've been on Discord since 2017 when I found a server in a YouTube video. Since then, I've been exploring the platform, building bots and servers of my own, and moderating groups like this one.

I've been hooked on Chrome OS since 2019, when I received my first device. Since then, I've started a collection of 3 devices, and have gotten my family on the Chromebook train.

In my free time, you'll often see me playing a game, or hanging out in the server. I'm happy to be here, and I'm hoping I'll be here for a long time.
